data.description: Charming brick home located in a quiet and friendly neighborhood. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area that boasts an abundance of natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room with the dining area, providing the perfect space for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with your loved ones. The bedrooms offer plenty of space for relaxation and privacy. The master bedroom includes an ensuite bathroom, providing a serene retreat after a long day. An additional office area can be used as your home office, game room, sitting room, etc., the possibility is endless. Situated on almost 1/4 acre, this property offers ample outdoor space for various activities. The backyard presents endless possibilities for gardening, outdoor dining, or simply enjoying the fresh air. Conveniently located with easy access to schools, shopping centers, parks, the airport, and beautiful beaches of Amelia Island.
